    <headline>Gale, yellow level, Andenes - Loppa, 22 March 15:00 UTC to 24 March 14:00 UTC.</headline>
    <description>Tuesday southwest occasionally strong gale force 9. Tuesday afternoon decreasing gale force 8, first in south. Late Tuesday evening decreasing west force 5. From early Wednesday morning southwest near gale force 7. Late Wednesday morning increasing strong gale force 9 m/s. </description>
    <instruction>Do not go out at sea in a small boat.</instruction>
